{"tid":951380,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米眾籌冬天必用產品 – 米家電暖器","createTime":"2018-12-22T09:56:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-22T13:03:26.000Z","uid":52215,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b17568cfef053635c7586e645d6b55b4b72a6af8","tid":951380,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:56:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LuYhetg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLuYhetg.jpg&h=9243fe3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nQooah<br />\n<br />\n小米眾籌冬天必用產品 &ndash; 米家電暖器<br />\n<br />\n冬天來了，尤其寒流侵襲的日子，除穿厚衣服外，家中的暖爐暖風機等都會拿出來的吧！<br />\n<br />\n不過有時候等暖爐及暖風機發熱，到整個室內都溫暖，都要花一段時間。所以，相信怕冷的人會十分心急。日前小米就宣佈將推出一款抗寒產品，名字叫「米家電暖器」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但是對於這款產品，小米卻沒有說明，只是發放出一張圖畫的海報。當中「熱得均勻熱得快 全屋保冷氣死角」的標語，外界估計採用歐美日韓國家比較流行的對流式電暖爐（上圖為「智米電暖器」）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n採用上下對流的方式進行散熱，首先加熱一部分空氣，然後採用熱空氣上升和冷空氣下降的原理，對室內空氣進行迴圈加熱。而且更可令室內氣溫上升更加快速和均勻。同時因為推動整個空間內的空氣流動，所以在加熱過程中不會有太明顯的風感，對於室內的空氣濕度影響也比較小。<br />\n<br />\n根據小米官方微博的資料，這款產品將於 12 月 26 日下午 2 時 30 分開始進行集資，但價格未有公佈。"},{"pid":"5911acaa0cedfd1932f2c48227558d21075dbf7a","tid":951380,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9394ae9155a652dd164da18eb46ff60f4b480034","tid":951380,"uid":52010,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"580f3ef1a944f0bf862788cbc9902e267ef97c0f","tid":951380,"uid":122570,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:18:35.000Z","msg":"洗撚用佢咩，大把幾舊水嘅暖風松都已經好好"},{"pid":"42c2313b219effb0fa3577424b7cc29bdd884900","tid":951380,"uid":163783,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:58:08.000Z","msg":"好想小米出隻小型+一體式暖氣（非電熱式）<br />\n<br />\n500$內"},{"pid":"5041fab648689d243a4ddc4c2919152b2e309b14","tid":951380,"uid":139538,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:58:36.000Z","msg":"買暖爐,仲要集資,痴左線<br />\n<br />\n豐澤,大把現貨暖爐賣"},{"pid":"c2c04dc6cd6de602eddcbed223b2dd90e72353c8","tid":951380,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T11:59:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8930a9b3ec9556bc72d8fc93b3e1b2444fce7c83","tid":951380,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"16b0d77ebe73d205f09715d3caacdf8fe3e13616","tid":951380,"uid":25003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8930a9b3ec9556bc72d8fc93b3e1b2444fce7c83","tid":951380,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5911acaa0cedfd1932f2c48227558d21075dbf7a","tid":951380,"uid":176063,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:18:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T12:57:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d4b3486b98e0f0f1713b3821c01f4b29b26cbf","tid":951380,"uid":181294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:00:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"10bca810ddb3a70929783738807d3a754a2d9291","tid":951380,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-22T13:03:26.000Z","msg":"核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}